Comment: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為妳已經是專業了
Comment: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們一直都...
Comment: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊 椎名一直都跑在我前面
Comment: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,連背影都完全看不到
Comment: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是... 看不到的不只有我
Comment: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回頭看的椎名也看不到我的身影
Comment: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,其實我啊
Comment: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也一直期待著喔
Comment: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,空太
Comment: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說不定可以收到巧克力什麼的
Comment: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上課時收到簡訊後就迫不及待想趕快放學
Comment: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真的?
Comment: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,收到巧克力很開心?
Comment: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為我是竹筍派的嘛
Comment: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太好了
Comment: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真白
Comment: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,感... 感冒的話就麻煩了 我們回去吧
Comment: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,空太 我可以牽你的手嗎?
Comment: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,果然還是算了
Comment: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那... 那算什麼啊?
Comment: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為...
Comment: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為冷靜不下來
Comment: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,心臟噗通噗通地跳個不停
Comment: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真白
Comment: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一直以來妳都好遙遠
Comment: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是現在...
Comment: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,空太
Comment: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,心臟跳個不停
Comment: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是因為妳活著
Comment: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,空太呢?
Comment: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,比真白還更加活蹦亂跳呢！
Comment: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們回來了
Comment: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,歡迎回來
Comment: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,青山 已經回來啦
Comment: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,甄選呢?
Comment: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把能做的都做了
Comment: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,馬上要吃飯了
Comment: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上井草學姐說是情人節餃子派對
Comment: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼情人節吃餃子...
Comment: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還勉強赤坂同學一起幫忙包餃子呢
Comment: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,七海
Comment: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,麗塔呢?
Comment: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,麗塔小姐?
Comment: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前食客女已經回去了
Comment: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,麗塔來過了?
Comment: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼都沒聽你說過 DRAGON
Comment: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為她好像很匆忙 沒辦法啊
Comment: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 都特地來到日本了
Comment: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是不是發生了什麼? 赤坂同學
Comment: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,算了 誰都會有一兩件不願說出的事情
Comment: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒什麼 麗塔一定馬上就會再來玩的
Comment: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總之 飯就是要趁美味的時候吃不是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,美咲學姊?
Comment: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說起來 仁學長的巧克力又扔掉了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說不定是這樣呢
Comment: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不管是誰 即使有多親近 多少也有不願說出的事情吧
Comment: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對了 青山早上所說的
Comment: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,神田同學 還記得約定嗎?
Comment: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,甄選如果順利通過的話
Comment: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到時候希望你能聽人家說話
Comment: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,最喜歡你了
Comment: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了? 神田同學
Comment: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有 沒有 沒有 沒有
Comment: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等等 那是我想太多了
Comment: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,青山怎麼可能對我
Comment: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼? 不過...
Comment: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,想要更明確
Comment: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,甜的和鹹的 想要分得明確點...
Comment: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,包了巧克力的餃子...
Comment: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喔 真白中獎了
Comment: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不可以亂玩食物 媽媽不是說過了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也有放大蒜進去的喔
Comment: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,臉色變好差
Comment: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不好吃
Comment: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,情人節餃子就是指這個嗎?
Comment: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT
Comment: 0,0:23:40.74,0:23:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們是宇宙人
Comment: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,宇宙裡有很多閃亮的星星
Comment: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣想著時 卻有種說不出話的感覺
Comment: 0,0:23:47.14,0:23:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們現在真的閃閃發亮著嗎?
Comment: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,

